data.description: WOW! ! There are many pleasant surprises within this property! Step into comfort and luxury nestled among lush mature pine trees. The entire lot is heavily adorned with freshened landscaping. Especially notice the walk out area has a lovely southwest view of the sunset. There are scenic walking trails in this dog friendly neighborhood! Enter through the modern glass doors into the uncommon charm of this open floor plan. Dining room to the right ready for entertaining your family and friends. Surrounding you with many windows and a charming light and airy atmosphere. The front bedroom has a cathedral ceiling and has been completely redecorated to follow current color trends. This area also could double as a den or home office, complete with a fully updated half bath that completes this area as a guest quarter. The great room is large, again with a beamed ceiling and huge windows. At the back of the home you will find a large owners retreat, complete with an updated walk-in -shower, with 2 shower heads a double sink vanity, twin medicine cabinets and a full sized stackable washer and dryer at your finger tips.The walk-in-closet is large and easily organized.There is a private entrance to the lovely sunroom with the picture perfect view, again this could be an office or den or an area to relax in after a busy day.The home has an outdoor deck and a screened porch area with electrical. To complete the circle of the main level is the sparkling clean white kitchen complete with high end Grable Cabinets, 42inch upper cabinets,soft close drawers,pull out shelves also a handy work station. Stainless steel appliances.This is all sitting atop a beautiful oak floor.There is abreakfast nook and double pantry to complete the area.  Stroll down the open stairway into the lower level. This area is perfect for entertaining . The room is large with a walk-out Slider doors open onto a lovely bricked patio.The rec room  has a wet bar and this level is completed with another bedroom with a full bath.That's not all there is a large unfinished area which holds another laundry with a deep utility sink. Stone steps lead back up to the front of the home with the fully landscaped yard.The association lake is just across the street. Pool and tennis courts make this a perfect find. Hurry before another weary home buyer snaps this up!
